HEADWORD: Trichoscolices
<hw>Trich`o*scol"i*ces</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos>
<ety>[NL., from Gr. <grk>tri`x</grk>, <grk>tricho`s</grk>, hair +
<grk>skw`lhx</grk> a worm.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>An extensive
